<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p>05</p>
<p>I was counting sheep all night.</p>
<p>我整晚都在数绵羊。</p>
<p>count sheep是习语，意为“失眠”;源自失眠时“数羊”可入睡之传说。</p>
<p>其他相关表达</p>
<p>06</p>
<p>I guess I drank too much coffee, I was wide awake all night.</p>
<p>我猜我喝太多咖啡了，睡不着。</p>
<p>07</p>
<p>Sleeping pills somehow didn't work for me last night.</p>
<p>安眠药都对我没用。</p>
<p>08</p>
<p>I've been suffering from insomnia.</p>
<p>最近我一直受失眠之苦。</p>
<p>09</p>
<p>I didn't close my eyes until early morning.</p>
<p>我一整夜都没合过眼。</p>
<p>今天的内容都学会了么?</p>
